WEBVTT

00:01.075 --> 00:02.278
Previously on
"The Originals"...

00:02.279 --> 00:03.918
Klaus: I assume
I have the misfortune

00:03.919 --> 00:05.020
of speaking to my mother.

00:05.021 --> 00:06.530
I have come to heal our family.

00:06.531 --> 00:09.157
I will undo everything
that has been done,

00:09.158 --> 00:10.999
thereby giving you a new life.

00:11.000 --> 00:12.337
You should get out of here.

00:12.338 --> 00:14.147
My brother is not
the forgiving kind.

00:14.148 --> 00:15.354
I'm not afraid of him.

00:15.355 --> 00:17.832
I'm about to get even with Klaus,
and you're gonna help me.

00:17.833 --> 00:18.968
You're the Alpha.

00:18.969 --> 00:20.808
Our people are not
meant to be slaves.

00:20.809 --> 00:21.946
You can free them.

00:21.947 --> 00:24.056
[Coughs] Ollie?

00:24.057 --> 00:27.134
I want you to rejoin our family,
take the body of a mortal,

00:27.135 --> 00:28.609
and we can all be happy again.

00:28.610 --> 00:30.080
- Niklaus...
- You're not real.

00:30.081 --> 00:32.389
I am flesh and blood,
your flesh and blood.

00:32.390 --> 00:33.897
You are my son.

00:33.898 --> 00:36.977
I brought him here to be
the father you never had.

00:36.978 --> 00:39.278
You said you wanted Elijah.
He's sleeping.

00:39.279 --> 00:42.355
When he wakes, he'll
make his own decision.

00:43.842 --> 00:45.773
You cannot catch me, Elijah.

00:45.774 --> 00:48.611
You're getting faster, Klaus,
but you're not yet fast enough.

00:48.612 --> 00:50.583
Ha ha!

00:51.621 --> 00:55.143
Klaus? Niklaus?

00:58.145 --> 01:01.376
Elijah: There you are.

01:01.377 --> 01:04.022
[Thunder]

01:11.679 --> 01:14.307
Do you understand?

01:17.118 --> 01:20.756
One day, only a monster
shall remain.

01:24.901 --> 01:28.473
[Elijah panting]

01:28.988 --> 01:30.745
Klaus: I know you
are locked in battle.

01:32.718 --> 01:34.355
Klaus, voice-over:
However deep in your mind

01:34.356 --> 01:38.026
our mother has set the stage,
hear my voice.

01:38.539 --> 01:41.625
Our mother thinks she will win
because she has left you alone,

01:41.626 --> 01:45.372
but you are not alone.

01:45.373 --> 01:49.508
Let me in.

01:49.509 --> 01:54.257
Let me help end whatever torment
she has forced upon you.

01:54.809 --> 01:56.009
Uh! Ah!

01:58.476 --> 02:00.977
Uh!
Oh!

02:00.978 --> 02:02.506
What are you doing?

02:02.507 --> 02:06.412
[Panting]

02:06.413 --> 02:10.824
I'm trying to enter Elijah's
thoughts to wake him.

02:10.826 --> 02:14.464
Esther has locked me out.

02:15.284 --> 02:18.975
Is this rash a side effect

02:18.976 --> 02:21.180
of the witchy acid trip he's on?

02:25.211 --> 02:28.664
I haven't seen this
since I was a child.

02:28.665 --> 02:30.367
Mikael would return
home from battle

02:30.368 --> 02:32.238
more blindly
temperamental than usual,

02:32.239 --> 02:34.479
and our mother
would use the petals

02:34.480 --> 02:37.264
of a rare Marelok orchid
to put him to sleep.

02:37.265 --> 02:39.850
She would mend his mind
with a spell

02:39.851 --> 02:43.931
and then wake him with
the roots of the same plant.

02:43.932 --> 02:47.001
If she has access to it now,

02:47.002 --> 02:49.484
then maybe it also
grows in the bayou.

02:49.485 --> 02:51.411
You stay here with your wolves

02:51.412 --> 02:53.193
and mind the fort.

02:53.194 --> 02:55.419
I'd rather rip
your mother's head off.

02:55.420 --> 02:57.617
Steer clear of her.

02:57.618 --> 02:59.494
I mean it, Hayley.

02:59.495 --> 03:01.632
She already got to you once.

03:01.633 --> 03:03.201
What would happen if
Elijah were to wake

03:03.202 --> 03:04.805
and find you a victim
of her madness?

03:04.806 --> 03:07.439
I won't go after her.

03:07.440 --> 03:09.875
I promise.

