03:18.286 --> 03:21.511
I've learned a few things
from your mother.

03:23.895 --> 03:26.460
I won't go after her.

03:28.030 --> 03:31.192
I'll go after
everything that she loves.

03:33.233 --> 03:36.914
Sync & corrections by <font color="#00ff00">Rafael UPD</font>
